{"tid":2493697,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【聽日就係】BNO英國選民登記4月19號截止","createTime":"2021-04-18T06:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T08:41:15.000Z","uid":305299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5fee422a31a7079551f16b9ae29f9f68995c8fe3","tid":2493697,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xxtTQAT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxxtTQAT.jpg&h=cd07a561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年5月英國就會舉行地方選舉，而且好多地區都會選出當地嘅警務處處長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(冇錯，選警務處處長，香港冇得選，但英國可以，正唔正?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 所以請到咗英國嘅BNO把握自己嘅權利，登記做選民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以下係選民登記要求：<br />\n<br />\n- 以合法身份通常居住英國 (有人未夠半年都成功登記)<br />\n- 英聯邦公民 (BNO就係其中一種)<br />\n- 夠18歲 (蘇格蘭同威爾士地方選舉可以16歲)<br />\n最下面有選民登記傳送門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">注意</span>：<ins>請善用身份剔除及匿名登記</ins></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗選舉嘅公正，以及畀政商界參考，英國政府係有兩本選民名冊：公開選民名冊 (open register) 同一般選民名冊 (electoral register) <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n顧名思義，公開名冊係啊豬啊狗都可以睇到，只要你肯畀錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />公開名冊係會列出你個名同地址，所以政客、商人、學者、記者等等都會時不時畀錢買來睇同研究，而依家依個時勢，唔排除會有英國以外嘅勢力都會想買來睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以建議，可以考慮選擇將自己嘅資料從公開名冊入面剔除 (opt out)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喺網上登記或者聯絡各地嘅選民登記辦事處就可以剔除身份，下面有傳送門，而且剔除公開名冊入面嘅身份係唔會影響投票權，所以可以放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而一般選民名冊就應該有齊每位選民嘅資料，但一般名冊就只有特定理由先可以睇到，例如：核對貸款申請、競選活動等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果都仲係有擔心，就可以透過匿名方式登記做選民 (registering anonymously)，咁樣就會兩本名冊都搵唔到你嘅資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但匿名登記就唔係人人都可以申請，而且申請程序比較複雜，一般係畀暴力受害者本人、佢嘅同屋人士申請，目的係費事被發現之後再次畀人尋仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過今時今日嘅局勢，可能有部份BNO都有咁嘅需要，細仔申請匿名登記嘅資格同手續請睇下面傳送門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n= = = = = 網上選民登記 = = = = =<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/register-to-vote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fregister-to-vote&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RG2%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=937f7524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/register-to-vote</a><br />\n<br />\n= = = = = 郵寄選民登記 = = = = =<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/register-to-vote-if-youre-living-in-the-uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fpublications%2Fregister-to-vote-if-youre-living-in-the-uk&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RG2%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=141e7e4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/register-to-vote-if-youre-living-in-the-uk</a><br />\n<br />\n= = = = = 剔除公開名冊資料 = = = = =<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/electoral-register/opt-out-of-the-open-register\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Felectoral-register%2Fopt-out-of-the-open-register&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RG2%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=8abc264f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/electoral-register/opt-out-of-the-open-register</a><br />\n<br />\n= = = = = 匿名選民登記 = = = = =<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/register-to-vote-anonymously\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fpublications%2Fregister-to-vote-anonymously&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RG2%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=95d9168b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/register-to-vote-anonymously</a><br />\n<br />\n= = = = = 單純些牙 = = = = =<br />\n香港監察呼籲抵英BNO盡早登記做選民<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2417828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2417828</a><br />\n<br />\n= = = = = 開心些牙 = = = = =<br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/p/ima_hksiuwaga肉豬/show/5ffc2e981b349a25f3104f28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2Fima_hksiuwaga%E8%82%89%E8%B1%AC%2Fshow%2F5ffc2e981b349a25f3104f28&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RG2%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=0001e9dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/p/ima_hksiuwaga肉豬/show/5ffc2e981b349a25f3104f28</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SjYTQCA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSjYTQCA.png&h=7aae3004&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c092020ef28e5b23011c8dcbdb844c91dec05f56","tid":2493697,"uid":193026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:10:58.000Z","msg":"行動post要推"},{"pid":"25349b87d2c4ad1933298c11bd6bce137e641dc6","tid":2493697,"uid":193026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:14:26.000Z","msg":"你地呢一刻做既嘢，將會決定最後搵唔搵到英國去救而家坐緊既手足<br />\n<br />\n要選到個代表到香港人既代議士<br />\n出聲去提英國，佢地當日賣我地香港人豬仔既結果，係呢班無辜既香港人要硬食"},{"pid":"e9c17c6b58e395fa9af4f991cc0191f1401f782f","tid":2493697,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c092020ef28e5b23011c8dcbdb844c91dec05f56","tid":2493697,"uid":193026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:10:58.000Z","msg":"行動post要推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T06:20:36.000Z","msg":"thx <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc2b8785e05cbbaa2031ae326b66cdcac494763a","tid":2493697,"uid":193026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9c17c6b58e395fa9af4f991cc0191f1401f782f","tid":2493697,"uid":305